sequenceDiagram
    participant Config as Configuration
    participant Container as MT5 Container Parser
    participant Element as Dedicated Element Parser
    participant Batch as Parsed Batch Ref

    Config->>Container: Resolve container parser + element parser
    Container->>Container: Receive known MT5 array type
    loop each element
        Container->>Element: Parse one known structure
        Element-->>Container: Parsed element result
    end
    Container-->>Batch: Parsed content batch ref
    Note over Container: No runtime parser dispatch inside loop
